34
00:11:21,847 --> 00:11:24,916
<i>(Recording) Please leave a message after the beep.</i>

35
00:11:24,918 --> 00:11:27,585
<i>[Beep] Hey, Dad, it's Chris.</i>
<i>(Sarah) Did you get him?</i>

36
00:11:27,587 --> 00:11:30,488
