<i>(Sarah) Why don't you try his cell?</i>

37
00:11:30,490 --> 00:11:33,458
<i>(Chris) 'Cause he doesn't have a cell.</i>
<i>(Sarah) You could email him.</i>

38
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:35,960
